name: Global X USD High Interest Savings ETF
longDescription: The ETF invests substantially all of its assets in high interest U.S. dollar deposit accounts with one or more Canadian  chartered banks. The ETF can also invest in high-quality, short-term (one year or less) debt securities, including U.S.  dollar denominated treasury bills and promissory notes issued or guaranteed by the United States federal government  or the Government of Canada, or their respective agencies, and U.S. dollar denominated bankers acceptances.
fulldescription: The ETF invests substantially all of its assets in high interest U.S. dollar deposit accounts with one or more Canadian  chartered banks. The ETF can also invest in high-quality, short-term (one year or less) debt securities, including U.S.  dollar denominated treasury bills and promissory notes issued or guaranteed by the United States federal government  or the Government of Canada, or their respective agencies, and U.S. dollar denominated bankers acceptances.  The ETF seeks to maximize monthly income for unitholders while preserving capital and liquidity by investing  primarily in high interest U.S. dollar deposit accounts with Canadian banks
